title: University Perspectives: Destination Graduation (University of Arkansas)
text: ( Source : University of Arkansas ) The course University Perspectives : Destination Graduation will be offered again in the spring 2016 semester. Now in its third year, the course is designed to assist incoming freshmen with the transition
